default11.13.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultIn order to counteract the lack of job stability, the employment structure of 
defaultmany 
defaultresearch groups should be modified. At the moment these consist of one group leader with a permanent position and a number of postdoctoral research associates (referred to a
defaults postdocs) on fixed term contracts, in addition to PhD students. We propose that the role of senior postdocs should be professionalized by the creation of the permanent role of “researcher” to be associated with groups. This is the structure of research g
defaultroups in other Countries such as Italy where the retention of women in STEM careers is much higher.
